originalText.text:
I no longer recall how I was referred to Dr.Auerbach but I am very grateful that I was referred to him.
If I had to describe Dr. Auerbach in one word it is compassion. You can feel the compassion he has for his patients. He is extremely intelligent which becomes obvious as he thinks through his analysis of a problem I bring him,  pointing to aspects I have never considered.
My therapy with Dr Auerbach has been extremely productive and fruitful
